{"tid":949552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【老竇帶個仔去死　男童慘被硬拉繼續過路】","createTime":"2018-12-21T01:29:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T10:49:41.000Z","uid":225464,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e58fe664831fea3c7b7e0b67e6ff55c11560fc68","tid":949552,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T01:29:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181221/bkn-20181221073043215-1221_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181221%2Fbkn-20181221073043215-1221_00822_001.html&d=DcGHbNw%2B4eT%2BJYIid6iYFjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=2237626a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181221/bkn-20181221073043215-1221_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iGidmqY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiGidmqY.jpg&h=6b9550da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>車輛狂砵　男童嚇到呆　慘被硬拉繼續過路</strong><br />\n<br />\n小朋友懵懂無知，家長應以身作則，教導孩子正確的觀念。惟近日元朗竟有男子在紅燈時，硬拉着小朋友衝過馬路！<br />\n<br />\n從Facebook群組「馬路的事討論區」的影片可見，周三（19日）下午約5時50分，當時青山公路元朗段近擊壤路交界的行人燈號正轉為紅色，不少途人停在安全島中等候。<br />\n<br />\n惟當車輛徐徐開出之際，一名平頭裝的男子竟然拉着男童橫過馬路。司機隨即響號煞車，惟男子停頓一下後，緊拖着目瞪口呆的男童，繼續施施然過路。<br />\n<br />\n發貼者表示：「假如小朋友因為大人胡亂帶佢橫過馬路而出事，我一定會好唔安樂。」網友亦紛紛斥責男子所為：「轉咗燈都要死衝」、「係要扯住佢過」。"},{"pid":"b125cdc3a70e4b9c6cc7463a680950d28c8b652b","tid":949552,"uid":107364,"like":3,"dislike":21,"score":-18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T01:31:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc877b763f8d1131fe43dad0e20e4e62bde76715","tid":949552,"uid":89931,"like":13,"dislike":4,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"b125cdc3a70e4b9c6cc7463a680950d28c8b652b","tid":949552,"uid":107364,"like":3,"dislike":21,"score":-18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T01:31:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T01:33:21.000Z","msg":"你死全家未<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80fe0b0d1c2fb33d5f0aeaf2a025bf77b625af60","tid":94955